{"tid":976991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗被要求提供DNA助查強姦案","createTime":"2019-01-10T22:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T00:32:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b16e9b6e2dbd4d87b30c8ac3df834fcf1eea3fcf","tid":976991,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T22:53:05.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=rp4f%2BVw9sspe9bP%2BJ4vZNozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=125acd7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】美國拉斯維加斯警方，已正式要求被指強姦的祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度提供DNA樣本。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，意大利法院已收到拉斯維加斯警方的文書，要求基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）提供DNA樣本，看看是否跟聲稱被強姦女子一條裙子上的DNA脗合；BBC則引述C朗的律師，指這只是「例行程序」。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月底，德國《明鏡周刊》指今季轉戰祖雲達斯的C朗於2009年6月時，在拉斯維加斯強姦美國女子Kathryn Mayorga，並在事後給予掩口費。C朗當時已堅決否認，指對方是為了博出名而誣告他，但由於Kathryn Mayorga提出訴訟，拉斯維加斯的警方已展開調查。"},{"pid":"64bed95255448be096e68759b72254e5a37932d9","tid":976991,"uid":197319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"條裙keep咗9年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"31ebb04c6e8e7d466c55f640c23631e5efdc61fc","tid":976991,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64bed95255448be096e68759b72254e5a37932d9","tid":976991,"uid":197319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"條裙keep咗9年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T23:33:46.000Z","msg":"咩啊咪之前果個咩告完和解再metoo果個啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efb92ac159222c37c34dc7e2ca887dbe382c0ce","tid":976991,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"31ebb04c6e8e7d466c55f640c23631e5efdc61fc","tid":976991,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64bed95255448be096e68759b72254e5a37932d9","tid":976991,"uid":197319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim